{"tid":2002691,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"兩休班警涉非法聚賭被捕　屯門工廈Party Room變牌九檔","createTime":"2020-05-05T10:36:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-05T11:09:35.000Z","uid":20933,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"7bb9643b4c1c7e56b9123d8c362ee6755446c849","tid":2002691,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T10:36:20.000Z","msg":"警方昨日（4日）於屯門一間工廈Party Room，拘捕多人於上址涉嫌非法聚賭，當中包括2名休班警員。<br />\n<br />\n消息指，警方昨日於屯門建泰街恒威工業中心一個派對場地進行突擊巡查，發現上址多人聚賭，包括打麻將及牌九等，警方拘捕36人涉嫌非法聚賭，並發現其中2人為現職警員，分別是52歲及33歲，各自隸屬屯門警區軍裝巡邏小隊及大埔警區刑事調查隊。"},{"pid":"83368f06591128e0c96ad5592efbbc485f5ca811","tid":2002691,"uid":199893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T10:46:56.000Z","msg":"笑到仆街"},{"pid":"4c2b60a61db30af3e055d2d81e920f6ca64d3f8f","tid":2002691,"uid":341608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T10:48:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e537c9961f1863b336ae91f314baee76eca5bf4d","tid":2002691,"uid":121197,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T10:55:01.000Z","msg":"屌你老母自己人呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d730e41bab5323727f077f4f235aedc6eb324b7","tid":2002691,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T10:57:38.000Z","msg":"陀地睇場？"},{"pid":"0781ea93c5db04ec9ae70187685d049441320047","tid":2002691,"uid":254594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T10:59:59.000Z","msg":"做乜拉9我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n自己友呀屌你老母<br />\n你跟邊個架？我跟屠輝既"},{"pid":"db14dfc35310d4a586e98b72a4c37d17a8a9cc9d","tid":2002691,"uid":190897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T11:0